php-chuid (0.6.0) trusty; urgency=low

  * Dropped PHP 5.2 support;
  * Added support for cgi-fcgi and cli-server SAPIs with ZTS enabled
  * Drop supplementary groups on setgid()
  * Better detection of DocumentRoot
  * Added tests
  * Fixed memory leaks on errors
  * Refactoring
  * Absense of capabilities generates only E_CORE_WARNING
  * Dropped force_gid feature

 -- Volodymyr Kolesnykov <volodymyr@wildwolf.name>  Fri, 17 Oct 2014 08:05:00 +0300

