php-chuid (0.5.0-ppa1) quantal; urgency=low

  * Removed stealth mode completely
  * chuid can be loaded both by extension and zend_extension;
    chuid automatically disables itself when ZTS is enabled but
    SAPI is neither cli nor cgi
  * Fixed many old bugs

